OL,3,CWater commission should support new
OL,4,Creservoir in East Kent, says Tory MP
OL,6,FSir Roger Gale has been campaigning
OL,7,Ffor a new reservoir in East Kent for
OL,8,Ffour decades
OL,10,FConstruction of a new reservoir in
OL,11,FEast Kent must be supported by the
OL,12,Fnewly established Independent Water
OL,13,FCommission, according to a local
OL,14,FConservative MP.
OL,16,FSir Roger Gale told ITV News Meridian
OL,17,Fthe government-backed body should
OL,18,F"throw its weight behind" plans to
OL,19,Fbuild the water storage facility at
OL,20,FBroad Oak near Canterbury.
