OL,3,CWater commission should support new
OL,4,Creservoir in East Kent, says Tory MP
OL,6,FThe project has been in the pipeline
OL,7,Ffor decades and was most recently
OL,8,Fsubject to a public consultation in
OL,9,Fearly 2023, with officials hoping it
OL,10,Fcould be operational by 2036.
OL,12,FSir Roger said: "I've been campaigning
OL,13,Ffor it for 40 of my 41 years and I
OL,14,Fhope the commission may throw its
OL,15,Fweight behind it."
