OL,3,CWater commission should support new
OL,4,Creservoir in East Kent, says Tory MP
OL,6,F"We're building houses across East
OL,7,FKent. We can't go on building houses
OL,8,Fwithout water. We need that reservoir
OL,9,Fand if we take the decision to build
OL,10,Fit tomorrow, it'll still be 10 years
OL,11,Fbefore it's there," Sir Roger added.
OL,13,FThe Broad Oak reservoir scheme could
OL,14,Fhold more than 5,000 million litres of
OL,15,Fwater, enough to supply 22 million
OL,16,Flitres of water a day, according to
OL,17,FSouth East Water.
