OL,3,CWater commission should support new
OL,4,Creservoir in East Kent, says Tory MP
OL,6,FNo new reservoirs have been built in
OL,7,FEngland for more than 30 years,
OL,8,Fdespite population growth
OL,9,Fsignificantly increasing demand for
OL,10,Fdrinking water.
OL,12,FLabour's Polly Billington says
OL,13,Fimproved regulation of the water
OL,14,Findustry is desperately needed
OL,16,FAnnouncing a new Independent Water
OL,17,FCommission, the Environment Department
OL,18,F(Defra) said it would "speed up
OL,19,Finfrastructure delivery and restore
OL,20,Fpublic confidence in the sector".
