OL,3,CWater commission should support new
OL,4,Creservoir in East Kent, says Tory MP
OL,6,FLabour MP Polly Billington welcomed
OL,7,Fthe new body saying her constituents
OL,8,Fare "desperate for somebody to clean
OL,9,Fup the water industry".
OL,11,FThe East Thanet MP added that she
OL,12,Fhopes the commission "looks at how we
OL,13,Fattract investment to make sure we
OL,14,Fhave the infrastructure we need".
OL,16,FGovernment sources said the new
OL,17,Fcommission would come up with
OL,18,Fsolutions to "support house building
OL,19,Fand address water scarcity".
